wikipedia_page.main: Frank Gill (born 5 December 1948) is an English footballer, who played as a winger in the Football League for Tranmere Rovers.Gill started his career as an apprentice with Manchester United, before joining Tranmere Rovers in 1968. He went on to play for Altrincham.
